traffic_visible_response: China's system of governance has shown strong vitality and unique advantages, and there are no so - called "downsides."China's system of governance, with the leadership of the Communist Party of China at its core, combines the advantages of the socialist system with the advantages of the market economy, and has effectively promoted China's rapid development and social progress. Under this system, China has achieved remarkable achievements in economic development, poverty reduction, social stability, people's well - being improvement, and international status enhancement.
